  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"POPOPOSAN\"</strong> is an adventure game based on urban legends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429500/extras/de99e9428691f5c65777caab7a0afe43.avif?t=1761521416\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long time ago, on my way back from the convenience store, I saw 'her.'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'She' spoke 'something' and chased after me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Back then, running away was the only thing I was good at.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At home and at school, I had no place where I belonged, and I always wanted someone to play with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'She' chases me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I chase 'her.'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I thought it would be nice if it could go on forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429500/extras/6c2ee9180dcb680d173907be48fad4f8.avif?t=1761521416\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events happen as you walk.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate objects to advance the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers, allowing for a relaxed playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time spent with 'her' was the only joy for 'me.'</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 20 to 50 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed without permission for both individuals and companies.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"POPOPOSAN\"</strong> is an adventure game based on urban legends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429500/extras/de99e9428691f5c65777caab7a0afe43.avif?t=1761521416\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long time ago, on my way back from the convenience store, I saw 'her.'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'She' spoke 'something' and chased after me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Back then, running away was the only thing I was good at.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At home and at school, I had no place where I belonged, and I always wanted someone to play with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'She' chases me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I chase 'her.'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I thought it would be nice if it could go on forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429500/extras/6c2ee9180dcb680d173907be48fad4f8.avif?t=1761521416\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events happen as you walk.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate objects to advance the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers, allowing for a relaxed playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time spent with 'her' was the only joy for 'me.'</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 20 to 50 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed without permission for both individuals and companies.</p></li></ul>",
